function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	

	-- Activate Arena Light
	tLights = Hydra.ActorsInGroup(idArenaLights)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(tLights[1]) then
		Hydra.ActorEnable(tLights[1])
		Hydra.Wait(0.1)
		Hydra.ActorDelete(tLights[1])
	end
	
	-- Delete the trigger, so that it doesn't fire again (same idea as one-shot on the trigger gizmo, i'm just used to doing it this way)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idActorDetector)

end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete("CAP_Tier5_Kehj_Hell_ThroneOfHatred_Boss")
	
	------------------------------------------------------
	-- First Time Rewards
	
	local tAllPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	
	for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tAllPlayers) do
		-- Drop the TreasureClass, which contains both "always" and "first time" rewards
		-- The First Time stuff is conditioned by the flag that is set after the drop occurs
		Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idActorKilled, "FirstTimeReward_Capstone_UberLilith", idPlayer)
		
		-- Set the variable, to mark that this player has recieved a reward
		Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idPlayer, "FirstTimeReward_Capstone_UberLilith")
	end
	
	------------------------------------------------------
	
	
end
